\end{document}where k
f and k
b are the formation and breaking rate constants and [Re], [An], and [ReAn] are, respectively, the concentration of receptor, analyte, and receptor-analyte complex. The thickness of the layer grown on the sensor surface due to the binding of analyte molecules to the receptor, ?w, depends on the receptor density, ?
